==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unarm
<hw>Un*arm"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To put off, or lay down, one's
arms or armor.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧I'll <xex>unarm</xex> again.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unarmed</ent>⟦br⟧
